snippet.title: King's League II - Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Get it now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/996080/Kings_League_II

Lead your team to victory! Recruit, train and manage fighters of different classes before entering tactical battles of wit and glory. In this sequel to an award-winning strategy simulation RPG, can you climb the King’s League?


Enter the King’s League and prepare yourself for battle!

King’s League II is the sequel to the award-winning strategy simulation RPG. Recruit and manage fighters of different classes before entering tactical battles of glory. Lead your team to victory and climb the most prestigious League in Kurestal!

King's League II Official Website
https://thekingsleague.com

King's League on Facebook 
https://www.facebook.com/playkingsleague

King's League on X
@PlayKingsLeague
